 playing at night</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Awesome pearl activated power ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An absolute banger of a soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395450/extras/Newboardclear.gif?t=1739053759\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1395450?t=1739053759","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395450/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739053759","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739053759","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739053759","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":1437590,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395450/extras/Remote_playcropped.gif?t=1739053759\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether your friends are nearby or far away, you can play together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiplayer is locally supported using either controllers or only your keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steam Remote Play can be set up easily. Follow the Steam guide to learn more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"